48. Record number handling in PHP with suitable examples.
CODE:
<?php
$students = ["Alice", "Bob", "Charlie", "David"];

// Get total number of records
$totalRecords = count($students);

echo "Total Students: $totalRecords\n";

// Display each record with its record number
foreach ($students as $index => $name) {
    echo "Record " . ($index + 1) . ": $name\n";
}
?>
OUTPUT:
Total Students: 4
Record 1: Alice
Record 2: Bob
Record 3: Charlie
Record 4: David
